                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5316" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0354</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8681 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">修武功 群侠戮力，闯功名 榜上争锋 ——游戏化管理赋能丰晖激励机制创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Play Harder，Win Better ——The Gamification Management in Fenghui</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李晓梅，李劭峰，邓祝钧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">丰晖生物科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">游戏化管理；人力资源管理；丰晖；疫情；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gamification Management; Human resource management; Fenghui</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着90后员工成为职场的中坚力量，传统管理模式逐渐失去良好的激励作用，如何激发90后员工潜能成为新时代人力资源管理的焦点问题。湖南丰晖生物科技有限公司实行了自行设计的游戏化管理，并发展壮大。即使在2020年新冠疫情下，仍能借游戏化管理推动员工间沟通交流。本案例通过“江湖武侠”游戏的形式展现了丰晖游戏化管理运行环境、具体措施、升级完善和新冠疫情背景下的运行状况，描述了游戏化管理推动下90后员工的工作表现和企业绩效，引导学生在分析90后员工特点和需求基础上，运用三因素激励理论探讨游戏化管理与90后员工工作需求的契合程度，并据此分析丰晖游戏化管理的可行性、创新性、升级原因和未来方向，为对90后员工的管理提供思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With post-90s employees becoming the backbone of the workplace, the traditional management mode gradually lost a good incentive role. How to stimulate the potential of post-90s employees has become a big problem in the new era. The Hunan Feng Hui Biotechnology Co., Ltd. has implemented the self-designed gamification management and has been developing gradually. Even in the context of the outbreak of the COVID-19 in 2020, it is still able to maintain the operation of the gamification management with the help of the network and strengthen the communication between employees at home. Through the story of Jianghu, this case introduces the environment, specific measures, the development of Fenghui&#39;s gamification management and its operation situation under the background of the outbreak of the COVID-19. It describes the work performance of the post-90s employees and the enterprise performance under this management. It guides students to analyze characteristics and needs of post-90s employees and uses the three factor incentive theory to discuss the fit degree of the gamification management and the work demand of post-90s employees.So that they can explore the feasibility, innovation, upgrading reasons and the future of the gamification management to provide new ideas for the management of post-90s employees.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">激励；管理创新；组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-04</td>
                            </tr>
